Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This sun is awfully hot for 9:00 in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.97,0:01:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so, this is just the thing to refresh my rotted brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.57,0:01:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be reborn, starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a revolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.62,0:02:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,One to keep this girl smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.48,0:02:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.70,0:02:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,my journey with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.43,0:02:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a new departure for just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What the... What's up with that gloomy group?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's ominous, for a new departure on a clear day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting. Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.96,0:02:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, hold on, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hana-Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.53,0:03:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So, she knows these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:16.84,Background2,,0,0,0,,Uh, this is a guy I knew from high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's this "Hana-Hana" stuff? And she was meeting them here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're not taking a vacation just the two of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:19.29,Background2,,0,0,0,,And when I told him about today's offline meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:20.61,Background2,,0,0,0,,he said he wanted to take part.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.61,0:03:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is that guy, the one you talked about on the forum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's all right. Well, shall we get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.98,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&HD9B6C7&\3c&HFFEAFF&\shad0\an2\frz14.319\pos(657.977,154.286)}Akira Jogasaki
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This boat belongs to you, Mr. Minegishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time I've been on one of these, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.95,0:05:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you really did own a cabin cruiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you rather I'd been lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.01,0:05:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were a lie, the offline meeting itself would have been called off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? We've come all this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.09,0:05:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't call it off now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry up and go to this island of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There are parts of our talk last night that I don't remember exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Where was it we're going again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,An uninhabited island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an island privately owned by "Mr. God", I guess his real name is Mr. Minegishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He says it has a very lovely sandy beach
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's just like Paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.64,0:06:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,An appropriate place for us now, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.99,0:07:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.29,0:07:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnSegoe\fax-0.075\shad0\bord0\c&HADA5A4&\pos(623.334,457.5)\frz7.764}Hitomi
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Jogasaki, we're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, hit it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This means we should be able to wrap this up today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit early, but let's all grab lunch together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take care of the rest ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's left is all simple work,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,so there's no need for you to use up your time looking over it, Mr. Jogasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:07:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You have plans with your girlfriend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Hitomi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The cellular phone you are calling is either in a locale without cellular service or is turned off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, we placed a reservation recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, if it's been cancelled, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.80,0:09:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:09:59.45,Note,,0,0,0,,An Introduction to the Study of Poisons
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a dock here and everything, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, a wealthy capitalist once had a summer home here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought it from his relatives who put it up for an Internet auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen a real private beach before!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a revolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.74,0:11:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The only ones here are Senpai and those other three.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to be afraid of strangers looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It truly is Paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't! Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I, too, tentatively declare I'll participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I plan to drink at a high-school friend's place tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't contacted him yet, but since he's a hikikomori, it's for certain he's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.16,0:11:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I've known him a long time, so I have to say goodbye to him beforehand anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:53.06,Note,,0,0,0,,Address: 202 Mita House, Kawasaki City, Kanagawa Prefecture
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize if I drink too much and I'm late. You can leave without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Hot-hot-hot-hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're not going to swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.23,0:12:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, seems like last night's alcohol is still with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the story with these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.17,0:12:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming all this way to the beach and not even swimming...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't an offline meeting a place to be more rowdy and have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is nothing but a gathering of hikikomoris.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, that includes me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No! This summer I'll be reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! It's a revolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.19,0:12:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,First thing is to make friendly talk with the people I just met today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:13:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a high-level technique a hikikomori couldn't possibly pull off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He ignored me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, the new Sato isn't going to be discouraged by something like being ignored once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What game are you playing? I play a lot too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I play gal-games though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a younger friend who knows all about games; he's a real game otaku... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I say something inappropriate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, the new Sato doesn't get discouraged by this kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had a revolution after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes, I'll get it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, I assumed I'd get that sort of reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax, New Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.48,0:13:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai told me before that you're a medical student.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a former medical student.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't attend school anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.81,0:14:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, that may have been a touchy subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I said that, I'll expose something shameful about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the fact is, I'm a hikikomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.24,0:14:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose there's some medicine that could make me feel super-energetic?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have some, I'd love for you to share it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.43,0:14:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If I gave you that potent a medicine without a prescription,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,it'd be a violation of the pharmaceutical laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, there's no medicine to cure a hikikomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He really doesn't have to talk as bluntly as that when somebody's just trying to be friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there still something you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't necessarily have to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I have other people to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! That older guy will talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.66,0:15:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax, Sato, it's a revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you drink one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Mr. Minegishi, with that boat and this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.77,0:15:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How can a person acquire stuff like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.07,0:15:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,As someone with life experience, please tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point of asking that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The... The point...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true I've acquired things ordinary people couldn't acquire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But in exchange, I lost so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Like an ordinary person's happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still want to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.11,0:16:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I wanted that desperately to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ex-Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,With this many human beings around...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,why am I so lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.95,0:16:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I came all the way out to this island paradise...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.01,0:16:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(1855,2355,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}...even though it's our last Culture Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.79,0:16:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I wonder if that's also how the class rep felt back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be quiet! Homeroom isn't finished yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:42.10,Background2,,0,0,0,,This is our last Culture Festival, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember that was the time we were deciding what to put out for the Culture Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:45.06,Background2,,0,0,0,,So, let's all make it an amazing one that"ll be a great memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My noisy classmates were ignoring the class rep, who was struggling all by herself, and I was among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you so worked up about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the assertiveness of youth?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.89,0:16:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:17:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time, I thought it was cooler to be detached.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.39,0:17:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was detached toward studying, toward romance, toward friendship...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And the conclusion of all that was life as a hikikomori, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato! Get up, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already past noon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The first day of the Comic Stall is gonna be over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! I can't believe I overslept on this crucial day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.11,0:18:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You're that girl Sato knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.45,0:18:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.93,0:18:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Sato come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Did Sato go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop joking around, please. He's a hikikomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way he could go all alone to a place with so many people like the Comic Stall, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.13,0:18:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He went with a woman in a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That was somebody else you saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.67,0:18:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way he has anyone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.99,0:18:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There is one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were Hitomi Kashiwa from the Literature Club,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,he might go off somewhere with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is what you just said true?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.81,0:18:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you be willing to tell me a few more specifics?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.67,0:19:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.11,0:19:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd collect some driftwood and have a campfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.32,0:19:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's interested in that kind of thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.72,0:20:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.49,0:20:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break... Well, what can you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, I remembered the original purpose of this offline meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.59,0:20:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.65,0:21:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason we all gathered together in a place like this
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,was that we thought we'd spend at least the last day of our lives pleasantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"The last day of our lives"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This... This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi may be taking part in this offline meeting with Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.58,0:21:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Offline meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The Island Nearest to Paradise?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:38.65,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60.504\fnCambria\b1\c&H050505&\shad0\bord0\frz14.925\pos(715.505,458.319)}Let's end our lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.26,0:21:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.30,0:21:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They intend to end their lives today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.55,0:21:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Se-Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:21:59.96,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5A99F8&\pos(640,136.135)\fs60.504}Episode 12
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:21:59.96,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2170F4&\pos(640,468.907)\fs60.504}Welcome to the Offline Meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.72,0:21:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody told me about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.98,0:23:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a hikikomori, more pathetic than a stray dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.01,0:23:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already too late to turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.94,0:23:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.51,0:23:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode, "Welcome to Paradise!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.30,0:23:39.88,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&HD7B8E6&\pos(640,113.445)\fs60.504\fad(570,0)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.30,0:23:39.88,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&H916BE2&\pos(640,446.219)\fs60.504\fad(570,0)}Welcome to Paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:16.18,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,I lift my eyes a little and look into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:19.26,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,All I do is mutter every time,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.33,0:00:22.31,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,as I turn my back
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.31,0:00:24.64,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,on this perfect everyday life
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.64,0:00:27.81,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,"Where am I supposed to go?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:32.86,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,With you who are giving me a look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:42.20,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,In the shadows of a back alley,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.12,0:00:49.33,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,the hands of a clock repaint the time that has been stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:53.07,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,Extended hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:57.44,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,puzzle pieces that don't fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:01.74,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,Until the abandoned two
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:05.79,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,reunite with something
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:10.42,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,that has been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:13.96,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,Recover
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:18.22,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,the last piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.09,0:01:24.35,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,and let's start walking.
